targets.rawSql: SELECT commit_id as commit_id, commit_message, gpu_name FROM benchmarks WHERE branch = '${branch}';

SELECT CAST(m.measurements->'first_eager_forward_pass_time_secs' AS double precision) AS first_eager_forward_pass_time_secs, left(b.commit_id, 7), m.time FROM benchmarks as b JOIN model_measurements AS m ON b.benchmark_id = m.benchmark_id WHERE b.branch = '${branch}' AND gpu_name = '${gpu_name}'

SELECT CAST(m.measurements->'second_eager_forward_pass_time_secs' AS double precision) AS second_eager_forward_pass_time_secs, left(b.commit_id, 7), m.time FROM benchmarks as b JOIN model_measurements AS m ON b.benchmark_id = m.benchmark_id WHERE b.branch = '${branch}' AND gpu_name = '${gpu_name}'

SELECT CAST(m.measurements->'time_to_first_token_secs' AS double precision) AS time_to_first_token_secs, left(b.commit_id, 7), m.time FROM benchmarks as b JOIN model_measurements AS m ON b.benchmark_id = m.benchmark_id WHERE b.branch = '${branch}' AND gpu_name = '${gpu_name}'

SELECT CAST(m.measurements->'time_to_second_token_secs' AS double precision) AS time_to_second_token_secs, left(b.commit_id, 7), m.time FROM benchmarks as b JOIN model_measurements AS m ON b.benchmark_id = m.benchmark_id WHERE b.branch = '${branch}' AND gpu_name = '${gpu_name}'

SELECT CAST(m.measurements->'time_to_third_token_secs' AS double precision) AS time_to_third_token_secs, left(b.commit_id, 7), m.time FROM benchmarks as b JOIN model_measurements AS m ON b.benchmark_id = m.benchmark_id WHERE b.branch = '${branch}' AND gpu_name = '${gpu_name}'

SELECT CAST(m.measurements->'time_to_next_token_mean_secs' AS double precision) AS time_to_next_token_mean_secs, left(b.commit_id, 7), m.time FROM benchmarks as b JOIN model_measurements AS m ON b.benchmark_id = m.benchmark_id WHERE b.branch = '${branch}' AND gpu_name = '${gpu_name}'

SELECT
  d.cpu_util,
  d.time
FROM
  benchmarks AS b
  JOIN device_measurements AS d ON b.benchmark_id = d.benchmark_id
WHERE
  branch = '${branch}'

SELECT
  b.commit_id,
  d.gpu_util,
  d.time
FROM
  benchmarks AS b
  JOIN device_measurements AS d ON b.benchmark_id = d.benchmark_id
WHERE
  branch = '${branch}'
SELECT d.mem_megabytes, d.time FROM benchmarks AS b JOIN device_measurements AS d ON b.benchmark_id = d.benchmark_id WHERE branch = '${branch}'

SELECT
  d.gpu_mem_megabytes,
  d.time
FROM
  benchmarks AS b
  JOIN device_measurements AS d ON b.benchmark_id = d.benchmark_id
WHERE
  branch = '${branch}'

list.definition: SELECT created_at - INTERVAL '5 secs' FROM benchmarks WHERE branch = '${branch}' ORDER BY benchmark_id ASC LIMIT 1;
list.name: StartTime
list.query: SELECT created_at - INTERVAL '5 secs' FROM benchmarks WHERE branch = '${branch}' ORDER BY benchmark_id ASC LIMIT 1;

list.definition: SELECT time + INTERVAL '5 secs' FROM benchmarks AS b JOIN device_measurements AS d ON b.benchmark_id = d.benchmark_id WHERE branch = '${branch}' ORDER BY b.benchmark_id DESC, d.measurement_id DESC LIMIT 1;
list.name: EndTime
list.query: SELECT time + INTERVAL '5 secs' FROM benchmarks AS b JOIN device_measurements AS d ON b.benchmark_id = d.benchmark_id WHERE branch = '${branch}' ORDER BY b.benchmark_id DESC, d.measurement_id DESC LIMIT 1;
